Package mk.musiclibraryweb.models

package mk.musiclibraryweb.models
This package contains the model classes for the music library WEB application. It includes classes for managing songs, handling song lists, and a custom exception.
Version:
5.0
Author:
Michal Kaminski
  • Class
    Description
    SingletonModel
    SingletonModel is a class that implements the Singleton design pattern for managing a single instance of SongList.
    Song
    The Song class represents a musical track with information about its ID, title, composer, album, release date, and duration.
    SongList
    The SongList class manages a collection of Song objects, providing methods to add, delete, and retrieve songs.
    SongTitleChecker
    A functional interface for checking the uniqueness of song titles.
    WrongInputException
    The WrongInputException class is a custom exception that indicates an invalid input has been provided.
